description: This header file declares functions for managing a receipt list in an OVSDB (Open vSwitch Database) API. It provides function prototypes for adding, processing, and clearing receipt entries, and includes relevant external dependencies.

methods.name: receipt_list_add
methods.description: Adds a receipt entry to the receipt list with the given receipt ID and callback.

methods.name: receipt_list_process
methods.description: Processes a receipt identified by the given receipt ID using the provided JSON result.

methods.name: receipt_list_clear
methods.description: Clears all entries from the receipt list.
